---
title: Easy Chicken Strips & Carrot Couscous Salad with Dill-Parsley Yoghurt
description: This ModOz-inspired meal features classic Aussie spices in an easy marinade for tender chicken breast, while carrot and parsley
bring colour and flavour to couscous. Sit back and enjoy this delicious delight from your friends across the ditch.
